title: þoaton 1.0
description:
þoaton - a music engine.
Heavily inspired by FS Studio and BeepBox, þoaton (say 'th-OH-tohn') is a music engine capable of 10 sounds, various pitches, and 'slide' notes (they aren't really slide notes, but it's 1.0, I'll add it to þoaton soon anyway)


























































































































































This thing was underdeveloped :/
instructions:
Click numbers 0-9 on your keyboard to change the sound of a block.
Click SPACE to place a block.

If a sound isn't working when you boot þoaton up, try changing the sound using 0-9. That usually helps!

title: PhysicsForm
description:
-CONTROLS-
Click the buttons to interact.
  - Button Number 1 is the 'Add Clone' button.
  - Button Number 2 is the 'Switch Costume' button.
  - Button Number 3 is the 'Record' button (you can tell if you're recording actions if there's a red dot next to the play/pause button)
  - Button Number 4 is the 'Create Action' button. (Press SPACE to add a new action)
  - Button Number 5 is the 'Play/Pause' button. (It pauses gravity, not animation!)
Click and Hold the shape in the centre of your canvas to move it around.

-NOTES-
This 'game' is better on full screen. Just be aware of that when you're playing.
There is a one second delay to the record button so you have time to get set up. Note that for when you're making a movie!
You have to triple click the record button when you're done recording. It's a bug, but I might leave it in the next version...

title: PicoChat
description:
PicoChat - a safe way to communicate.
Because you have free speech and can say some nasty stuff on the Scratch comment system, I've created a platform where you can message safely. Just click the maximise button, click it again, and you can message off a whitelist!
(New Scratchers can't use this due to the use of cloud variables)
Click 1 to switch to Pico mode.
Click 2 to switch to Tera mode.
Happy messaging!

Also, be careful of what you say- everyone online (on PicoChat) can see The Spread, so if you do catch someone being unkind on The Spread, let me know on my accounts,
@Gifboythegamer10 and @trashcanrobber6.

Originally shared August 3rd, 2025.

title: PATAPON 4
description:
PATAPON 4 is the new (fan-made) PATAPON game in the trilogy.
Advance, Jump, Attack and catch the Fever in this remix of the original series and with some new additions! Change level within a level if you're ever in a pinch- mobile support if you're playing on mobile-  the list goes on!

PATAPON 1, 2 and 3 is courtesy of Sony Entertainment, Playstation and Bandai Namco, Pyramid and Japan Studio. Credits to them for creating PATAPON!
CatOS is made by @Gifboythegamer10.
instructions:

title: BioNeer
description:
[BEHIND-THE-SCENES STORY]
So, this project was supposed to be a collaboration with @PenguinPal25, but he told me to start it off to launch the project off; we never found time to work on this project together, so I kept working and working on it until today. He's (hopefully) going to work with me on future updates, but only time will tell.

[CONTROLS]
Walk into biological organisms to pick them up and add them into your BioDex.
Press SPACE to open your BioDex, and press space again to close it.
Use arrow keys to walk.

[UPDATE LOG]
13/07/2025 - Initial Release.

[NOTES]
Please give me feedback if you want, or suggest ideas that you want to be added to the game. I'd be happy to reply or (maybe) add them.

[CREDITS]
Myself for all assets, all code and idea.
@PenguinPal25 for leaving me all alone in the dust. (joke)

title: the atomic level - a GSOL game
description:
-NOTICE-
This was made crazy fast (usually 30mins over 4 days)- this may be riddled with bugs and unsatisfactory to you guys, the consumers. So yeah, be warned. Also there's not a lot of context to the story in-game so there's that too, but if you YOU want to fill in the gaps, either read on to the 'Context/Story' section or remix and make your own story up!

-CONTEXT/STORY-
It's one fine day inside your hydrogen atom, and one second you're sleeping on your bond bed, next you're facing the leader of an army of invaders to defend your home. (End of current story)

-CONTROLS-
Left and Right to Move
A and D to Move
Space (When you have Grapple Hook in Inventory) to use Grapple
[0] to switch to Neutrono (Blue)
[1] to switch to Protona (Red)

title: records - An Indie Game
description:
Welcome to OrderRec Inc!
Here, you'll check records
for us and pass them or not
for the SAFE check.
Good Luck!

-CONTROLS-
Click on the Tick and Cross Buttons to pass through letters.
Flashcards (as seen at the end of the game) are events.
Make sure to pick the right button and look at the letters when passing through mail!

-HINTS- 
Hover over the letter if there's a flap - there's hidden, gamebreaking stuff behind the little flap.
